  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5217c218617d2b01.jpg?v=1782533537\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>One of the coolest things about holding my \"best of\" paper pack from Michaels is realizing that I have had enough \"hits\" to create such a thing! It features papers from all 6 of my collections with American Crafts and is available in stores now! The paper pad retails for $19.99, but is a \"hot buy\" and apparently drops to $5 regularly. For 60 papers - 3 sets of 20 different designs - it's a hot buy indeed.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/499df10930f7db94.jpg?v=1782533540\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>The paper pack is a great mix of favorite patterns in a size (8.5\"x11\") not available anywhere else. It's fun combining papers from the first signature line, Sketchbook, Ready Set Go, Yes Please, Cut &amp; Paste and Plus One.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9ed9dcd679530eb5.jpg?v=1782533543\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><strong>GIVEAWAY IS CLOSED, THANKS FOR YOUR SWEET COMMENTS!</strong> If you want to get your hot little hands on this Michaels exclusive, please leave a comment below. Internationals welcome. A winner will be chosen Friday, August 1 at 7am and notified. Thanks and good luck! The winner is #200 - Michelle Stokes says: July 31, 2014 at 3:07 am I would LOVE one of these packs!! We won’t be able to get our hands on them here in Australia so hoping Im a lucky winner this way!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! - Congrats!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}